Package Model.Tanks

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColorChangerTimer
    Timer that is responsible for changing damage tank color.
    Projectile
    Class that is responsible for every projectile object.
    ShootDelayTimer
    Timer that is responsible for projectile cooldown.
    Tank
    Class that is responsible for the actions of the neutral/enemy tanks.
    TankPlayer
    TankPlayer is responsible for visualization and animation of player tank.
    TankSecondPlayer
    TankSecondPlayer is responsible for visualization and animation of second player tank.
